# The build context is the repository root (see docker/docker-bake.hcl).
# Keep host build artifacts out of the context: Dockerfile.web's `COPY web/ ./`
# would otherwise overlay the host node_modules over the image's
# `bun install --frozen-lockfile` result, and Dockerfile.loadgen's
# `COPY loadgen/ ./` would ship the host target/ directory to the daemon.
.git
.docker-cache
web/node_modules
web/dist
loadgen/target
